{"tid":1981811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【獅城「淪陷」】新加坡新增1426宗確診創單日新高 淪東南亞疫情最多國家 麥當勞全停業","createTime":"2020-04-21T01:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T15:05:30.000Z","uid":23833,"like":181,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":122,"replies":[{"pid":"12c64fe51eefc75e214786307d42e31bab2cdbf4","tid":1981811,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:23:01.000Z","msg":"新加坡周一單日的確診個案再創新高，今午新增1,426宗，令確診個案增至8,014宗，超過印尼的6,575宗和菲律賓的6,259宗，成為病例最多的東南亞國家。外籍勞工仍然是主要感染群，而當地麥當勞上周也出現感染群，累計有7宗病例，麥當勞周日突然宣佈暫時關閉全部分店，是當地麥當勞首次全面停業，民眾趕緊吃「最後的早餐」，外賣訂單急升。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周日新增的596宗新增病例中，包括566名工作准證持有者。另有30宗屬本地社區病例，其中25人是本地公民或永久居民，5人是工作證件持有者。衞生部文告指出，新增的社區病例已有所減少，從前周的平均每天37宗，減至過去一周的平均每天31宗。<br />\n不過，沒住宿舍的確診工作准證持有者也持續增加，從之前的平均每天11宗，增至過去一周的平均每天21宗。政府周日透過電子憲報宣佈，把兩個外籍勞工宿舍列為隔離區，當地目前已有18個宿舍被列為隔離區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200420/MFV3SMVZIWNVR4SNGJO2I5VB5I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200420%2FMFV3SMVZIWNVR4SNGJO2I5VB5I%2F&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=969205eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200420%2FMFV3SMVZIWNVR4SNGJO2I5VB5I%2F&h=97ac15a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200420/MFV3SMVZIWNVR4SNGJO2I5VB5I/</a>"},{"pid":"a73332994c7c491fa7706bbdb940219341294b31","tid":1981811,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:26:18.000Z","msg":"🙈"},{"pid":"be4f60f541ada167a3a56b45095f088517b74688","tid":1981811,"uid":35752,"like":114,"dislike":0,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:27:47.000Z","msg":"猴城<img src=\"/